```

Suggest defining a helper to remove some of this repetition:

```
def normalize(path, prefix):
  return path if os.path.isabs(path) else os.path.join(prefix, path)
```

In a comment mention the rationale behind doing this and explain why other functions are not overridden:
```
def __add__(self, t)
def __setitem__(self, i, v)
```
